    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's looking for a great new home! It\u2019s been well-loved and is in really solid shape, running smoothly and ready for many more adventures. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a road trip, this car is super reliable and a joy to drive. Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have!",
