    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, providing exceptional power delivery and tactile feedback. This example features documented subframe reinforcement and a recent rod bearing service, addressing key chassis and internal engine longevity concerns. The suspension retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics with refreshed bushings, ensuring the car tracks true through high-G corners. A mechanically robust driver\u2019s car with a well-preserved interior and minor, honest road wear consistent with its mileage.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
