      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This example features the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Technical highlights include a documented rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe\u2014essential for long-term chassis rigidity. The suspension remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup delivers precise turn-in. While the finish shows minor cosmetic patina typical of a driven enthusiast car, the drivetrain is robust, having recently undergone a comprehensive valve shim adjustment. A turn-key performer for the driver who prioritizes mechanical integrity and analog feedback.",
